lead_paragraph: South Korea's Eun Jeong Seong and Italy's Virginia Elena Carta set up the first all-international U.S. Women's Amateur final in 106 years Saturday — and guaranteed a rare season sweep.

headline.print_headline: Seong, Carta Advance to US Women's Amateur Final
